<resources>
    <string name="app_name">Discover Meals</string>

    <string name="help_how_to_use">&#160;Select the ingredients which you like, tap the button
        and get the meals that contain them. The meals with the max number of matches will be
        on the top of the list, so you always will get the most relevant search result.</string>

    <string name="how_to_manage_ingrs">On the app start screen scroll up or down,
        choose category of your ingredient and scroll left or right to find it on the card.
        Tap the ingredient you wish once to select it. Your choice will be stored to the
        \«Chosen ingredients\» section.</string>

    <string name="help_how_to_like">&#160;Just tap the heart on the right upper corner of the meal
        recipe. From this moment it is saved to your \«Favourite meals\» section of the drawer menu.
    </string>

    <string name="help_how_to_search">&#160;No problem, just use \«Search meal\» section.
        Start to enter the name and the required meal will appear at once.</string>

    <string name="help_clear_ingrs">&#160;Open \«Chosen ingredients\» of the drawer menu,
        tap the ingredients you wish to clear and press the remove button. Also you can clear
        an each selected ingredient by tap it again on the start screen.</string>

